Totally have a love/hate relationship with this game. I absolutely adore the gameplay and amount of content this offers and I also like some parts of the story, but this could and should have been so much more. It feels incomplete and didn't answer the questions we fans wanted. You could say that we expected a masterpiece and "only" got a great game.
